Create and Share the App

Create an app from the Revenue Management for Financial Services Cloud template.
Navigate to CRM Analytics Studio, click Create, select App | Create App from Template, open the template selector, select Revenue Management for Financial Services Cloud, click Continue, Review the app preview page, click Continue, Select Create a brand new app, and then click Continue.
Enter a name for your app, and then click Create. 
After the process is complete, refresh the page to see your app.

To share the app with users:
Open your app in CRM Analytics Studio, add user names on the Give Access tab of the share window under Invite others, select their level of access: Viewer, Editor, or Manager.
Save your changes.
title: Creating and Sharing CRM Analytics Apps
